data.description:
You'll love this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home now available in the Desert Oasis community of Surprise! Home features lush landscaping and gas fire pit, new HUNTER DOUGLAS shutters throughout home, beautiful BONUS room with new HARDWOOD flooring and custom BARN DOOR can be used as 4th bedroom, office, playroom etc. New dog run w/turf, new Samsung Range w/Air Fryer, new shed, back patio misters/fans/lights...so many new upgrades to this well-cared-for 8-year-old home, making it BETTER THAN NEW. Garage has a tandem bay for a smaller 3rd car or additional storage. SOLAR powered with VERY low bills and some months even run at a credit. Close to schools and parks. Schedule your showing TODAY!

Refrigerator will be ordered and installed after move in. 

Backyard features a newer hot tub that is currently drained for safety reasons. Tenant is welcome to fill and use but is responsible for upkeep and maintenance. 

Owner will allow one dog, no cats. Must complete pet screening and provide proof of vaccinations. 

*BEWARE OF SCAMS! We do not list our homes on Craigslist or Facebook Marketplace. Please contact Stratton Vantage Property Management to confirm availability and rent price*
 
INITIAL MOVE-IN COSTS
Security-Deposit - minimum is 1.25X monthly rent but not greater than 1.5X the monthly rent. (75% may be refundable)
First Month Rent + 3% Processing Fee + Rental Tax where applicable + $75 Resident Benefit Package Setup Fee
Lease Preparation Fee: $225
*Pets - If Applicable, a minimum Non-Refundable Pet Fee in the amount of $250 per pet is required - (Some Breed Restrictions Apply) Does Not Apply to Assistive Animals
*Pets - If Applicable, the First Month of Pet Rent in the amount of $60-$80 per pet depending on type of pet(s) which includes a $30 pet administrative fee (Some Breed Restrictions Apply) - Does Not apply to Assistive Animals
 
RECURRING MONTHLY COSTS
Rent + 3% Processing Fee + Rental Tax (where applicable)
$75 Resident Benefit Package - (includes renters' insurance, credit reporting, rewards program and more)
*Pet(s) If Applicable, $60-$80 per pet, which includes a $30 pet administrative fee Does Not apply to Assistive Animals
 
 
*BEFORE YOU APPLY TO RENT THIS PROPERTY, PLEASE VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO REVIEW OUR RENTAL QUALIFICATIONS AND LEGAL DISCLOSURES 

ADDITIONAL DISCLOSURES 
Brewer & Stratton Property Management LLC is an Arizona Limited Liability Company dba Stratton Vantage Property Management. 
12-month minimum lease term, (longer lease terms may be negotiated).
Stratton Vantage Property Management does business in accordance with the Fair Housing Act. 
Stratton Vantage Property Management does not discriminate against any person based on race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin. 
The information contained in this ad is accurate to the best of our knowledge. 

Stratton Vantage Property Management is not responsible for any error or omission in the wording or content of this information.

Amenities: RANGE/OVEN, MICROWAVE, DISHWASHER, ICE MAKER, WATER SOFTENER, FRIDGE
